# Classic-Arcade-Game-Clone
 -HTML5 Canvas, Object Oriented JavaScript, CSS, HTML
 Arcade Game version 1.0 04/29/2017

 PROJECT DESCRIPTION
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 The goal of the game is to reach water avoiding collision with enemies. This project has basic game functionality and covers Object-Oriented JavaScipt concepts and HTML5 Canvas.

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Installing

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Specific procedures are not required. Right click on file, pick 'Open with...', chose your preferred browser.
 Can see the output by double clicking on index.html.
 To edit editor like sublime text, notepad++ or atom is required.
 Chrome dev tools are to be used for testing.

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 How to play
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Use arrow keys to navigate the character. You can move up, down, left, right.
 Navigate the character to avoid collision with bugs.
 Colliding with bugs causes game reset to initial character position.
 Reach water to win the game
 Good Luck! and have fun!
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Game folder files:

 - style.css - css file for index.html.
 - images (folder)- contains images required to run the game.
 - js (folder):
   - app.js - javascript file to provide object essential functionality
   - engine.js - provides general program functionality
   - resource.js - simple image loading utility
   - index.html - HTML file providing basic DOM structure for the program.
   - readme.txt - Game and overall program description
